creator: Nexudus Ltd
descriptionHtml:
LABS was created to empower and support businesses of any sizes. Our mission is to provide the right environment for your business to grow. With state-of-the-art spaces which foster innovation and productivity through the use of technology – each location is optimised for progression.

LABS is creating campus style coworking spaces in central locations, with premium design, curated community events and state-of-the-art technology. You don’t have to be tech-savvy to sign up. Our secure and sophisticated technology works seamlessly in the background, so you can focus on what you do best. Work. Play. Grow
descriptionShort: LABS was created to empower and support businesses of any sizes.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- You can now create and join Zoom meetings directly from feed threads, private messages and bookings

- Bug fix impacting custom fields
